19. h4 Bxh4 20. g3 Bg5 21. f4 exf4 22. gxf4 Bh4+ 23. Kd1 $44) 19. h4 $1 Bxe3 ({
Taking on h4 clearly favours White:} 19... Bxh4 20. exf5 Bxf5 (20... gxf5 $4
21. Qh5 $18) 21. Nxf5 Rxf5 22. g3 Bg5 (22... Be7 23. Bb5 $1 $16) 23. Bd3 Rxb3 (
23... Rf8 $2 24. Rxh7+ Kxh7 25. Qh5+ Kg7 26. Qxg6+ Kh8 27. Qh7#) (23... Rf7 24.
Bxg6 Rg7 25. Be4 $16 Rxb3 $140 26. Bxh7 Rxh7 27. Rxh7+ Kxh7 28. Qc2+ $18) 24.
Bxf5 gxf5 25. Qc2 Qb8 (25... Rb5 26. Qxf5 $18) 26. O-O $16 {Black doesn't have
sufficient compensation for the exchange, since apart from threatening to take
on f5, White also threatens 27.Nb4.}) 20. Qxe3 fxe4 (20... f4 $5) 21. h5 ({
Nothing is achieved by} 21. Qxe4 Ne7 22. h5 Nxd5 23. Bxd5 {in view of} Rf4 24.
Qd3 Rxa4 25. bxa4 Qg5 26. O-O (26. hxg6 $2 Qc1+ $19) 26... gxh5 {[%cal Gh5h4,
